## Development Workflow

### Git Workflow

- Feature branches: `feat/<short-description>-frontend`
- Bug fix branches: `fix/<short-description>-frontend`
- Commit messages in English, imperative mood: `Add appointment booking form`
- Keep branches small and focused. One PR per logical change.

### Development Scripts

```bash
# Install deps
npm install

# Dev server
npm run dev

# Type check
npm run type-check

# Lint
npm run lint

# Run tests
npm run test

# Run tests with coverage
npm run test:coverage

# Build for production
npm run build

# Preview production build
npm run preview
```

### Code Quality

- Run `tsc --noEmit` and `eslint src/` before committing — enforced via pre-commit hooks.
- Prettier formats on save via editor integration and on commit via pre-commit.
